msgid "It does pass! Let’s add another test, this time asserting that a smaller\nrectangle cannot hold a larger rectangle:"
msgstr "Il a réussi ! Ajoutons maintenant un autre test, qui vérifie cette fois qu'un\npetit rectangle ne peut contenir un rectangle plus grand :"

#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch11-01-writing-tests.md:587
msgid "```rust,noplayground\n{{#rustdoc_include ../listings/ch11-writing-automated-tests/no-listing-02-adding-another-rectangle-test/src/lib.rs:here}}\n```"
msgstr "```rust,noplayground\n{{#rustdoc_include ../listings/ch11-writing-automated-tests/no-listing-02-adding-another-rectangle-test/src/lib.rs:here}}\n```"

