#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch11-01-writing-tests.md:647
msgid "```console\n{{#include ../listings/ch11-writing-automated-tests/no-listing-03-introducing-a-bug/output.txt}}\n```"
